title: FNAF Blocks BETA
description: Ever wanted to recreate a FNAF restaurant in MINECRAFT? Well now you can do it with FNAF Blocks! (currently only those of FNAF 1 are available), soon more blocks

title: Fredbears Family Diner Dany Fox.MCADDON MCPE Bedrock
description: A strange restaurant full of giant robots supposedly made with the intention of children comes to your hands in the form of a playable addon for single-player and multiplayer! Fredbear's Family

title: Five Nights At Freddy's 2 Add-on
description: With this add-on adds content based on the horror video game Five Nights At Freddy's 2, adds the animatronics of the game, new decorations to create your own Freddy's pizzeria and much more

title: Five Nightat Freddy's 2
description: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 is a point-and-click survival horror game. Players take on the role of a night security guard who must complete their shift without being caught by the homicidal animatronic characters that wander through the building.

title: Five Nights At Freddy's BehaviorPack
description: With this add-on adds content based on the Five Nights at Freddy's video game where you can create your own Freddy's Fazbear pizzeria, interactive decorations, have your animatronics as decoration, you can also become one and in your Minecraft world will appear animatronics wanting to attack you.

title: FNAF addon MCPE
description: FNAF addon MCPE in Minecraft PE

title: Functional FNaF Security Breach Map
description: Not only are there these areas to explore, but I decided to take the project one step further and make the entire Pizzaplex functional, just like how it is in Security Breach.
